      *  MSGHNDDCL - Declares for Message Handler Call                *
      *                                                               *
      *  This include member declares the fields used by *DSP modules *
      *  in calling the message handler, ZAMSGHNDLE.  It requires that*
      *  the member ERR_ARRAYS is also included.                      *
      *                                                               *
